# Agency Website Development Plan

## AI-Powered Development & Automation Agency

---

## BRAND DIRECTION

**Agency Name Suggestion:** use "NexForge" — Claude will use it throughout)\_

**Tagline:** "We Build Smarter. We Automate Everything."

**Aesthetic Direction:**

- Dark theme with electric accent colors (cyan or lime green)
- Futuristic, tech-forward, high-contrast
- Clean but bold — not corporate, not playful
- Feels like a premium tech company, not a freelancer portfolio

**Fonts:**

- Display: Syne or Clash Display (bold headlines)
- Body: DM Sans or Neue Haas (readable, modern)

**Color Palette:**

- Background: #0A0A0F (near black)
- Primary Accent: #00F5C4 (electric cyan)
- Secondary Accent: #7B61FF (violet)
- Text: #F0F0F0 (off white)
- Muted: #888899 (gray for subtitles)

