## SITE STRUCTURE — 7 SECTIONS (Single Page)

---

### SECTION 1: HERO

**Purpose:** Instantly communicate who you are and what you do.

**Content:**

- Navigation: Logo | Services | Work | About | Contact [CTA Button]
- Big headline (2 lines):
  > "We Build Digital Products.
  > Powered by AI Automation."
- Subheadline:
  > "Full-stack development meets intelligent automation — helping businesses ship faster and work smarter."
- Two CTA buttons:
  - [Start a Project] — primary
  - [See Our Work] — secondary ghost button
- Background: Animated particle mesh or grid lines with subtle glow

**Claude Instructions:**

```
Build a dark hero section with a large two-line headline using Syne font.
Add an animated CSS grid/particle background. Include a sticky navbar with
logo on left and nav links on right. Two CTA buttons — one solid cyan (#00F5C4),
one ghost outline. Add a scroll-down indicator arrow at bottom.
```

---

### SECTION 2: SERVICES

**Purpose:** Show exactly what you offer — make it feel premium.

**Content — 4 Service Cards:**

1. **Full-Stack Development**
   - Icon: Code brackets
   - Description: "We build fast, scalable web apps, APIs, and SaaS products using modern frameworks — from MVP to production."
   - Tags: Next.js · Node.js · Supabase · React

2. **AI Integration**
   - Icon: Brain/circuit
   - Description: "We embed AI into your product — chatbots, LLM pipelines, smart search, content generation, and more."
   - Tags: Claude API · OpenAI · LangChain · RAG

3. **Workflow Automation**
   - Icon: Lightning bolt
   - Description: "We automate your repetitive business processes — lead handling, onboarding, reporting, and internal ops."
   - Tags: n8n · Make · Zapier · Webhooks

4. **SaaS Product Building**
   - Icon: Layers
   - Description: "From idea to launched product — we design, build, and deploy complete SaaS platforms for startups and businesses."
   - Tags: Architecture · Auth · Billing · Deployment

**Claude Instructions:**

```
Build a services section with a 2x2 grid of cards on desktop, 1 column on mobile.
Each card has: top icon, title, description, and tag pills at the bottom.
Cards have a subtle border with hover glow effect (cyan). Use glassmorphism
card style (dark bg with slight transparency and border).
```

---

### SECTION 3: HOW WE WORK (Process)

**Purpose:** Build trust — show you're organized and professional.

**Content — 4 Steps:**

1. **Discovery Call** — We understand your goals, stack, and timeline in a free 30-min session.
2. **Proposal & Scope** — You receive a clear plan, timeline, and fixed price within 48 hours.
3. **Agile Build** — We ship in 1–2 week sprints with demos after every milestone.
4. **Launch & Support** — We deploy, monitor, and support your product after go-live.

**Claude Instructions:**

```
Build a horizontal step-by-step process section with 4 steps connected by
a dashed line (desktop) or vertical line (mobile). Each step has a number
badge, title, and short description. Use staggered fade-in animation on scroll.
```

---

