---

### SECTION 5: WHY US (Differentiators)

**Purpose:** Answer "why hire you instead of someone else?"

**Content — 4 Points (icon + title + text):**

1. **AI-Native Team** — We don't bolt AI on. Every project is designed with AI from the ground up.
2. **Full-Stack + Automation** — Rare combo. One team handles dev AND automation — no coordination gaps.
3. **Fast Delivery** — MVPs in 4–8 weeks. We ship fast without cutting corners.
4. **Fixed Pricing** — No surprise invoices. You know the total cost before we write a line of code.

**Claude Instructions:**

```
Build a 2x2 stats/features grid with large icons, bold titles, and short
descriptions. Add a large background number or geometric shape behind each
card for visual depth. Section should have a slight background color shift
from the rest of the page (e.g. #0F0F1A).
```

---

### SECTION 6: TEAM

**Purpose:** Put faces to the agency — builds trust fast.

**Content:**

Intro line: "A focused team of 3 — no account managers, no middlemen. You work directly with us."

3 Team Cards:

- **[Your Name]** — AI Automation Expert · "I design and build intelligent systems that turn manual work into automated pipelines."
- **[Dev 1 Name]** — Full-Stack Developer · "I build scalable backends and APIs that power modern web products."
- **[Dev 2 Name]** — Full-Stack Developer · "I craft pixel-perfect UIs and seamless frontend experiences users love."

**Claude Instructions:**

```
Build a team section with 3 cards side by side. Each card: circular photo
placeholder, name, role badge, and short bio. Add a subtle colored border
per person (e.g. cyan, violet, white) to differentiate. Keep it clean and
minimal compared to other sections.
```

