### SECTION 7: CONTACT / CTA

**Purpose:** Convert visitors into conversations.

**Content:**

Big headline:

> "Ready to Build Something Smart?"

Subline:

> "Tell us about your project — we respond within 24 hours."

**Contact Form Fields:**

- Name
- Email
- Service Interest (dropdown: Development / Automation / AI Integration / SaaS / Other)
- Project Budget (dropdown: <$2K / $2K–$5K / $5K–$15K / $15K+)
- Message (textarea)
- [Send Message] button

**Side info:**

- 📧 hello@youragency.com
- 💬 WhatsApp link
- 🔗 LinkedIn link

**Claude Instructions:**

```
Build a full-width contact section with a two-column layout: left side has
the headline, subline, and contact info; right side has the form. Form inputs
are dark with cyan focus borders. CTA button is full-width solid cyan with
dark text. Add a subtle gradient glow behind the section.
```

